data.description: Welcome home to Laurel Mist Subdivision! This charming 4bedroom 4.5 bathroom full finished basement home features a plethora of different options. On the main level of the home you find an over sized owners suite, a separate office, half bath, laundry room, 2 car garage with the kitchen which offers stone counter tops, plenty of storage and boasts a large dining/breakfast area. From the kitchen you have eyes directly into the family area. Upstairs is home to 3bedrooms with carpet throughout and 2full bathrooms featuring tile floors. Downstairs you can find a fully finished basement with work/storage room, bonus room, bathroom, a second kitchen, and finally the media room which is perfect for hosting movie nights or sports gathering. On the exterior of this home you have a front porch and a screened back porch. This home offers ample amount of space for comfortable family living and entertaining. Home is less than 30 minutes away from Vines park, Tribble mill park, and stone mountain park with Plenty of shopping centers just minutes away from the home.Neighborhood amenities include a pool, tennis courts, and playground. Don't miss out on this opportunity!   ~Pictures coming soon~
